                     <p class="fs-md-16 fs-14">By navigating on our site, you agree that we can place cookie and web beacons on your computer or device. If you prefer not to receive web beacons, then you should stop using our site, or consult your browsing settings.</p>
                     

                     <h3 class="text-secondary fs-22 mb-3  font-weight-bold pt-4">
                         How to control cookies?
                     </h3>
